title: Ep 201 - Raju Srivastav Visits Gokuldham
shortDesc: Members of Gokuldham celebrate completing 200 episodes with Raju Srivastav. They have a few amazing dance performances lined up. Watch this episode to know what happens next.

title: Ep 202 - The Gadas Plan On A Trip
shortDesc: As Krishna Janmashtami is approaching, Daya requests Jetha to plan a trip to visit her family. Will Jetha agree to this? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 203 - Tappus Essay
shortDesc: Tappu writes an essay on the first showers of the year. Will his parents be impressed about it? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 204 - Jetha Lals Trip To London
shortDesc: Jetha gets an opportunity to go on a trip to London. Nattu Kaka thinks that he's the cause for this trip. What will Jetha say to this? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 205 - Raksha Bhandan At Gokuldham Society.
shortDesc: Jethalal is in a turmoil & wonders how to tell his family that they were not going to London. He decides to tell his family after the Raksha Bandhan event.

title: Ep 206 - London Trip Canceled
shortDesc: Jethalal finally takes the courage to inform his family at the breakfast table that the London trip was canceled.  Champaklal demands answers and asks if he was planning to go alone.

title: Ep 207 - Jethas Preparation For London
shortDesc: Jetha and his family are excited that he is going to London. Everyone is demanding for gifts from Jetha, which is slowly upsetting him. What happens next? Watch this episode and find out.

title: Ep 208 - Jethas Send Off
shortDesc: The members of the society including Jetha's family send Jetha off to the airport. Will the family be happy about Jetha's trip or not? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 209 - Jethas Digestive Pills
shortDesc: As Jethalal gets into the plane, Daya bhabi runs behind him to give him his digestive pills. Will Daya get into trouble for loving her husband?

title: Ep 210 - Sundarlal Helps Tappu Sena
shortDesc: Sundarlal visits Jetha's place and decides to help Tappu Sena regarding a financial matter. What is this favor that makes Tappu Sena jump with joy? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 211 - Dahi Handi Competition At Gokuldham
shortDesc: The members of Gokuldham Society celebrate Krishna Janmashtami together. They even arrange the famous 'Dahi Handi' Competition for which, there is a huge prize. Will Tappu Sena win the game?

title: Ep 212 - Prevention Against Swine Flu
shortDesc: As the deadly disease, swine flu is spreading, Daya has her own way of protecting herself from the flu. Watch this episode to know her theory.

title: Ep 213 - Bhide The Philosopher
shortDesc: Jethalal and his family have arranged for a bhajan session and Sonu is excited to help them along with the Tappu Sena. Meanwhile, Bhide gets deeply philosophical with his wife and starts to explain the purpose of life.

title: Ep 214 - Roshan Bhabis Party
shortDesc: The ladies of Gokuldham get together to discuss Roshan bhabi's party. During the conversation, Daya is reminded of Jetha's absence. What happens next? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 215 - Preparations For Ganesh Chaturti
shortDesc: As Ganesh Chaturti is approaching, Bhide sends an invitation to every house in the society. When Abdul gives the invitation to the Gadas, Champaklal sees the price everyone has to contribute and gets angry. What is the price fixed by Bhide?
